flowchart TD
    A[User] --> B[CLI Entry: agentic_rag.py]
    B --> C{Mode}
    C -->|build_index| D[Ingest Data]
    C -->|chat| E[Run Agentic Loop]
    C -->|evaluate| F[Run Batch Evaluation]

    D --> D1[data/pdfs -> pypdf]
    D --> D2[data/audio -> Whisper]
    D1 --> D3[Chunk Text]
    D2 --> D3[Chunk Text]
    D3 --> D4[Hugging Face Embeddings API]
    D4 --> D5[ChromaDB Persistent Vector Store]

    E --> G[Planner via Ollama]
    G --> H{Select Tool}
    H -->|search_knowledge_base| I[Query ChromaDB]
    H -->|inspect_project_file| J[Read local file preview]
    H -->|inspect_chat_logs| K[Read chat_logs.txt]
    H -->|finish| L[Stop planning]
    I --> M[Reflection via Ollama]
    J --> M
    K --> M
    M --> N{Evidence sufficient?}
    N -->|No| G
    N -->|Yes| O[Grounded Answer Generation via Ollama]
    L --> O
    O --> P[Append Agent Log]
    P --> Q[Return final answer]

    F --> R[Load evaluation_dataset.json]
    R --> S[Run agent for each question]
    S --> T[Score metrics]
    T --> U[accuracy | relevance | clarity | overall]
    U --> V[Print summary]

    W[Core Libraries] --> W1[requests: Ollama HTTP calls]
    W --> W2[chromaDB: vector database]
    W --> W3[huggingface_hub: embeddings]
    W --> W4[pypdf: PDF extraction]
    W --> W5[openai-whisper: audio transcription]
    W --> W6[python-dotenv: environment loading]
    W --> W7[tqdm: ingestion progress]

    X[How to run] --> X1[python agentic_rag.py --mode build_index]
    X --> X2[python agentic_rag.py --mode chat]
    X --> X3[python agentic_rag.py --mode evaluate --eval-file evaluation_dataset.json]
